A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 23 of Title 2 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, the "Georgia
2 Hemp Farming Act," so as to provide limits on the total concentration of THC and other
3 intoxicating cannabinoids in consumable hemp products; to revise provisions concerning the
4 certificate of analysis applicable to consumable hemp products; to provide criminal penalties;
5 to provide limits on the milligrams of THC and other intoxicating cannabinoids in
6 consumable hemp products in the form of gummies; to revise and provide for definitions; to
7 provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
8 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
9 SECTION 1.
